<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a2Jan1939"><font color="red">2 January 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on):  agree &hellip; safer to let you see further revised proofs of pages 257-320, so that you may be satisfied about the alinement of the side-notes &hellip; now asking our printers to &hellip; send you all further proofs direct &hellip; return the proofs &hellip; to me here &hellip; I was glad to have that sample of saffron colour that Mr Joyce wants to have for the binding. </div>
